title: fanoutqa: Who are the members of the current British Royal Family and who are their respective fathers? (a19574bcd377eda6)

chat_history.content: Who are the members of the current British Royal Family and who are their respective fathers?

The current British Royal Family consists of the following members:

- King Charles III - father: Prince Philip, Duke of Edinburgh
- Queen Consort Camilla - father: Bruce Shand
- William, Prince of Wales - father: King Charles III
- Catherine, Princess of Wales - father: Michael Middleton
- Prince George of Wales - father: William, Prince of Wales
- Princess Charlotte of Wales - father: William, Prince of Wales
- Prince Louis of Wales - father: William, Prince of Wales
- Prince Harry, Duke of Sussex - father: King Charles III
- Meghan, Duchess of Sussex - father: Thomas Markle
- Archie Mountbatten-Windsor - father: Prince Harry, Duke of Sussex
- Lilibet Mountbatten-Windsor - father: Prince Harry, Duke of Sussex
- Prince Andrew, Duke of York - father: Prince Philip, Duke of Edinburgh
- Princess Beatrice - father: Prince Andrew, Duke of York
- Princess Eugenie - father: Prince Andrew, Duke of York
- Prince Edward, Earl of Wessex - father: Prince Philip, Duke of Edinburgh
- Sophie, Countess of Wessex - father: Christopher Rhys-Jones
- Lady Louise Windsor - father: Prince Edward, Earl of Wessex
- James, Viscount Severn - father: Prince Edward, Earl of Wessex
- Prince Richard, Duke of Gloucester - father: Prince Henry, Duke of Gloucester
- Birgitte, Duchess of Gloucester - father: John Douglas Gordon Grandison
- Anne, Princess Royal - father: Prince Philip, Duke of Edinburgh
- Peter Phillips - father: Mark Phillips
- Zara Tindall - father: Mark Phillips
- Prince Edward, Duke of Kent - father: Prince George, Duke of Kent
- Katharine, Duchess of Kent - father: Sir William Arthington Worsley
- Princess Alexandra, The Honourable Lady Ogilvy - father: Prince George, Duke of Kent
- Prince Michael of Kent - father: Prince George, Duke of Kent
- Marie-Christine, Princess Michael of Kent - father: Günther, Baron von Reibnitz
- Prince George of Kent - father: Prince Michael of Kent
- Princess Helen of Kent - father: Prince Michael of Kent
- Prince Edward, Duke of Kent - father: Prince Edward, Duke of Kent
- Katharine, Duchess of Kent - father: Sir William Arthington Worsley

This list includes the main members of the royal family who are closely related to the monarch. There are other distant relatives, such as cousins and their families, who are part of the extended royal family but are not listed here.

Please note that this list might not reflect recent changes, such as births, marriages, or deaths, in the royal family.
